metadata.Plot: When John Hutton mysteriously awakens with no recollection of his past, yet with the ability to speak dozens of languages fluently, he decides to start a new life. Years later, he is sent tumbling down the proverbial rabbit hole after meeting another man that shares a similar condition and learning that there are several more individuals like him, all amnesiacs with extraordinary abilities. With the help of a private detective, John races against time before his past can rise up to destroy himself and his family.
